<article>
  <h1>Future</h1>

  <p>In the future we would like provide the following components, in no particular order:</p>

  <p class="note">
    This is not a roadmap and the order of creation might be different. 
    Also the list does not include all future ideas just a subsection.
  </p>

  <div class="max-w-sm mx-auto grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-2 items-start md:max-w-2xl lg:max-w-none mb-8">    
    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-xl h-full">
      <h3 class="high leading-snug tracking-tight mb-1">Uploader</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white text-center">
        A component to create upload mechanisms: allowing for parallel / serial uploads. 
        One idea is to also support or a "pool" of connections.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-xl h-full">
      <h3 class="high leading-snug tracking-tight mb-1">Progress</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white text-center">
        A component to create progress bars with, for network request, or article read percentages.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-xl h-full">
      <h3 class="high leading-snug tracking-tight mb-1">Search</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white text-center">
        A component to create search experiences with, should include debouncing, 
        local caching and filtering.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="relative flex flex-col items-center p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded shadow-xl h-full">
      <h3 class="high leading-snug tracking-tight mb-1">Pagination</h3>
      <p class="text-gray-800 dark:text-white text-center">
        A component to create pagination buttons with, supporting 
        the many pagination variants out there.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</article>